data.description: (4K seller’s closing cost incentive) Gorgeous 4-bedroom/ 3-bathroom (newly remodeled) home inside the beautiful resort-style residential living of Bellalago. This Paradiso model is located in a premium ¾ acre corner lot consist of a Large 40 X 15 saltwater pool with a 4-jet spa, Rheem electric heater and a Paradise Grill outdoor kitchen with a full-size grill, stove, 2 refrigerators, bluetooth stereo system and bar.     If you like to entertain friends and family the family room has a built in 7 Polk speaker surround sound system and the newly installed Masonite triple panel 10 feet tall French doors with built in blinds welcomes you into the oversized 30-foot wide lanai which provide you a vast 47’ X 31’ Screen enclosed pool area for you to enjoy the beautiful Central Florida summers, family barbecues and get togethers. This energy efficient property also comes with fully paid Aptos Solar Panels (115% capacity to the home) with a 30-year warranty, two solar edge inverters installed inside the garage, and a dedicated 20 AMP outlet in the garage for an electric vehicle. As soon as you pull up, the first thing you will notice is the beautiful curve appeal and lush landscaping along with the gorgeous pavers throughout the driveway along with the Spanish Mediterranean roof tiles giving it that elegant look. Master bedroom with hard wood look tile and an elegant recently remodeled master bath with a rainfall water shower. The elegant gourmet kitchen with 42-inch cabinets, double wall ovens, cook top, large center island with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances.     If that’s not all, Bellalago is within 30 minutes away from Walt Disney World and many major attractions. Bellalago community is a 24hr gated private community with our own Bellalago Academy, Flip Flops Restaurant/ Full pool side bar. Jr Olympic size pool, water park, kiddie pool, spa, full time staff and manager, fitness center and aerobics room, yoga and fitness trainers, fishing pier, boat dock and slip, walking and biking trails, basketball, tennis court, volley ball, barbecue area and too much to mention here. Must see it for yourself. Your home will feel as if you are on a life vacation. Video can be provided upon request.
